text: Cold are the crabs that crawl on yonder hills, Colder the cucumbers that grow beneath,
Colder the cucumbers that grow beneath, And colder still the brazen chops that wreathe
And colder still the brazen chops that wreathe%% The tedious gloom of philosophic pills!
The tedious gloom of philosophic pills! For when the tardy film of nectar fills
For when the tardy film of nectar fills%% The simple bowls of demons and of men,
The simple bowls of demons and of men, There lurks the feeble mouse, the homely hen,
There lurks the feeble mouse, the homely hen, And there the porcupine with all her quills.
And there the porcupine with all her quills. Yet much remains - to weave a solemn strain
Yet much remains - to weave a solemn strain%% That lingering sadly - slowly dies away,
That lingering sadly - slowly dies away, Daily departing with departing day
Daily departing with departing day%% A pea-green gamut on a distant plain
A pea-green gamut on a distant plain%% When wily walrusses in congresses meet -
When wily walrusses in congresses meet - Such such is life -
